{"tid":1092670,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「國」同「国」既分別","createTime":"2019-04-05T04:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T04:02:04.000Z","uid":224632,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5a353766190ce0d1f377da7a51fcd8af935236ac","tid":1092670,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:38:58.000Z","msg":"驟眼睇「國」呢個字其實係有「戈」、同「口」，同出面一個大「口」<br />\n即係有武器，同有人口，有城牆先有國家<br />\n<br />\n但而家個「国」字 ，乜都唔洗<br />\n<br />\n有「玉」字就夠，玉姐係玉璽<br />\n姐係有皇帝就夠<br />\n<br />\n而出面個大「口」，現今既社會已經無城牆，咁係咩？<br />\n係人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係唔話用文字黎灌輸思想都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他繁體字同殘體字既分別？"},{"pid":"f1cfafbe0a56d4d2c3a3e4ec0fe1a6991b071a3c","tid":1092670,"uid":44454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"愛同爱嘅分別，一個有心，一個冇心"},{"pid":"c9671ae556b08154b8f87a7604ce3e96a4c56721","tid":1092670,"uid":76834,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"愛 同 爱 <br />\n<br />\n愛要用「心」去感「受」<br />\n爱就係友就夠？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （殘字唔識解了）"},{"pid":"872df484dccd3a4c8b73257cb2a25aa520d49a73","tid":1092670,"uid":224632,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"f1cfafbe0a56d4d2c3a3e4ec0fe1a6991b071a3c","tid":1092670,"uid":44454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"愛同爱嘅分別，一個有心，一個冇心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"證明咗用殘體既人去交朋友唔講心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590cdc153ed0dc89fd25571bb0aad5b6403a7bb9","tid":1092670,"uid":63846,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"「国」好似係日本發明（好似係"},{"pid":"3c3489305a59dd92733a63fb2b1159ce032251f4","tid":1092670,"uid":29218,"like":1,"di